    "\"System\" follows the theme and text size set in your device Settings, including larger accessibility sizes." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the \"System\" theme.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"System\" folgt dem Design und der Textgröße, die in den Geräteeinstellungen festgelegt sind, einschließlich größerer Bedienungshilfen-Schriftgrößen."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Sistema\" sigue el tema y el tamaño de texto configurados en los Ajustes de tu dispositivo, incluidos los tamaños de accesibilidad más grandes."
          }
        },
        "fil" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Susundin ng \"System\" ang tema at sukat ng teksto na itinakda sa Settings ng iyong device, kasama ang mas malalaking accessibility size."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "« Système » suit le thème et la taille du texte définis dans les réglages de votre appareil, y compris les tailles d'accessibilité plus grandes."
          }
        },
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Sistem\" mengikuti tema dan ukuran teks yang diatur di Pengaturan perangkat Anda, termasuk ukuran aksesibilitas yang lebih besar."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Sistema\" segue il tema e la dimensione del testo impostati nelle Impostazioni del dispositivo, comprese le dimensioni di accessibilità più grandi."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「システム」は、デバイスの設定で指定されたテーマと文字サイズ（より大きなアクセシビリティサイズを含む）に従います。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"시스템\"은 더 큰 접근성 크기를 포함하여 기기 설정에서 지정한 테마와 글자 크기를 따릅니다."
          }
        },
        "ms" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Sistem\" mengikut tema dan saiz teks yang ditetapkan dalam Tetapan peranti anda, termasuk saiz kebolehcapaian yang lebih besar."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "«Система» использует тему и размер текста, заданные в настройках устройства, включая увеличенные размеры для специальных возможностей."
          }
        },
        "th" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"ระบบ\" จะใช้ธีมและขนาดข้อความตามที่ตั้งค่าไว้ในการตั้งค่าอุปกรณ์ของคุณ รวมถึงขนาดการเข้าถึงที่ใหญ่ขึ้น"
          }
        },
        "vi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Hệ thống\" sẽ theo giao diện và cỡ chữ được đặt trong Cài đặt thiết bị của bạn, bao gồm cả cỡ chữ trợ năng lớn hơn."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“系统”会遵循您设备“设置”中设置的主题和文字大小，包括更大的辅助功能字号。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "%@ hasn't been checked today yet. It checks in automatically, or open its details and tap “Check conditions” to check now." : {
      "comment" : "A body text that describes that the plant hasn't been checked today. The argument is the nickname of the plant.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "%@ hasn't been checked today. Move the sensor next to it and open its details to log a reading." : {
      "comment" : "A body text that describes what to do if the user has not yet checked a plant today. The argument is the nickname of the plant.",
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "%@ wurde heute noch nicht überprüft. Bringe den Sensor in ihre Nähe und öffne die Details, um eine Messung zu protokollieren."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "%@ no ha sido revisada hoy. Acerca el sensor a la planta y abre sus detalles para registrar una lectura."
          }
        },
        "fil" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Hindi pa na-check si %@ ngayong araw. Ilapit ang sensor dito at buksan ang mga detalye nito para ma-log ang isang pagbasa."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "%@ n'a pas encore été vérifiée aujourd'hui. Rapprochez le capteur de la plante puis ouvrez ses détails pour enregistrer une lecture."
          }
        },
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "%@ belum diperiksa hari ini. Pindahkan sensor ke dekatnya, lalu buka detailnya untuk mencatat pembacaan."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "%@ non è stata controllata oggi. Avvicina il sensore alla pianta e apri i suoi dettagli per registrare una lettura."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "%@は今日まだチェックされていません。センサーを近くに置いて詳細画面を開き、測定値を記録してください。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "%@은(는) 오늘 아직 확인하지 않았어요. 센서를 가까이 두고 상세 화면을 열어 측정값을 기록하세요."
          }
        },
        "ms" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "%@ belum diperiksa hari ini. Alihkan penderia berhampiran dengannya dan buka butirannya untuk merekodkan bacaan."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "%@ ещё не проверялось сегодня. Поднесите датчик ближе к растению и откройте подробности, чтобы записать показания."
          }
        },
        "th" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "%@ ยังไม่ได้ตรวจสอบวันนี้ ย้ายเซนเซอร์ไปไว้ใกล้ๆ ต้นไม้ แล้วเปิดหน้ารายละเอียดเพื่อบันทึกค่าที่วัดได้"
          }
        },
        "vi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "%@ chưa được kiểm tra hôm nay. Di chuyển cảm biến đến gần cây rồi mở chi tiết để ghi lại số liệu."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "%@今天还没有检查过。把传感器移到它旁边，然后打开详情记录一次读数。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
